column9: Confirmed negative: Patient negative based on testing performed at both Public Health Ontario (PHO) Laboratory and National Microbiology Lab (NML). Presumptive negative: Patient tested negative at PHO Laboratory but not yet tested by NML. Currently under investigation: Test results are pending. Presumptive positive: Patient tested positive at PHO Laboratory but not yet tested by NML. Confirmed positive: Patient positive based on testing performed at both PHO Laboratory and NML
